'''Bhumika Chawla''' (born '''Rachna Chawla''' on 21 August 1978<ref name=Chawla2015/>) is an Indian actress and a former model.<ref>{{cite news |last=Tanmayi |first=Bhawana |title='Missamma' enjoys her second innings |url=https://telanganatoday.com/missamma-enjoys-her-second-innings |date=15 September 2018 |newspaper=[[Telangana Today]] |access-date=14 March 2020}}</ref> She made her film debut in the Telugu film ''[[Yuvakudu]]'' (2000) and has since then worked in various Indian film industries and appeared in over thirty films in [[Cinema of Andhra Pradesh|Telugu]], [[Bollywood|Hindi]], [[Tamil cinema|Tamil]], [[Cinema of Kerala|Malayalam]], [[Kannada cinema|Kannada]], [[Bhojpuri cinema|Bhojpuri]], and [[Cinema of Punjab|Punjabi]]. Her notable performances include  ''[[Kushi (2001 film)|Kushi]]'' (2001) , ''[[Okkadu]]'' (2003), ''[[Tere Naam]]'' (2003), ''[[Missamma (2003 film)|Missamma]]'' (2003) , ''[[Sillunu Oru Kaadhal]]'' (2006) , ''[[Gandhi, My Father]]'' (2007) , ''[[Anasuya (2007 film)|Anasuya]]'' (2007) and  ''[[Buddy (2013 film)|Buddy]]'' (2013).

==Early life==
Chawla was born in a [[Punjabi people|Punjabi]] family in [[New Delhi]], India and completed her schooling there. Her father was an Army officer. Bhumika has two siblings, an elder brother and sister.

She moved to [[Mumbai]] in 1997 and started her career with Ad films and Hindi music video albums. She appeared in the [[Zee TV]] series ''[[Hip Hip Hurray (TV series)|Hip Hip Hurray]]''.

==Personal life==
Bhumika Chawla married her long-time boyfriend and [[Yoga]] teacher Bharat Thakur on 21 October 2007 at [[Devlali]], [[Nashik]] in a Gurdwara.<ref name="BT">{{cite web|url=http://www.screenindia.com/old/fullstory.php?content_id=17566 |title=Bhumika Chawla weds yoga guru Bharat |accessdate=21 October 2007 |publisher=Screenindia.com |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090124212050/http://www.screenindia.com/old/fullstory.php?content_id=17566 |archivedate=24 January 2009 }}</ref> She went regularly to Thakur's courses and is said to have dated him for four years, before eventually marrying him.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://entertainment.oneindia.in/telugu/top-stories/bhumika-weds-bharat-280907.html |archive-url=https://archive.is/20120708190248/http://entertainment.oneindia.in/telugu/top-stories/bhumika-weds-bharat-280907.html |url-status=dead |archive-date=2012-07-08 |title=Bhumika weds Bharath on Oct 25 th |publisher=[[Oneindia]] |accessdate=2009-08-06 }}</ref> The couple have a son born in February 2014.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telugu.cinemalead.com/news-id-bhumika-chawla-laddu-babu-28-02-143014.htm|title=Bhumika delivered a baby boy - Bhumika Chawla- Laddu Babu- Allari Naresh- Ravi Babu- Misama- Khushi - Cinemalead.com -|publisher=|access-date=3 March 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140303071716/http://www.telugu.cinemalead.com/news-id-bhumika-chawla-laddu-babu-28-02-143014.htm|archive-date=3 March 2014|url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.iqlikmovies.com/news/2014/02/28/Actress-Bhumika-Chawla-blessed-with-a-baby-boy/news/3396|title=Actress Bhumika Chawla blessed with a baby boy|author=iQlik Movies|work=iQlikmovies}}</ref>

